solution:
$$
\begin{gathered}
E = m_{0} c^{2}\left(1-\frac{v^{2}}{c^{2}}\right)^{-\frac{1}{2}} \approx m_{0} c^{2}\left(1+\frac{v^{2}}{2 c^{2}}\right) = m_{0} c^{2} + \frac{1}{2} m_{0} v^{2} \\
\frac{1}{2} m_{0} v^{2} = E - m_{0} c^{2} = T \\
v = \sqrt{\frac{2 T}{m_{0}}}
\end{gathered}
$$

For an isolated system, $E^{2}-c^{2}p^{2}$ is an invariant for all inertial reference frames, remaining constant before and after the decay. The calculations are done using the $\pi^{+}$ rest frame, which is also the center-of-mass frame.

$$
\begin{aligned}
&m_{\pi}^{2} c^{4}=\left(E_{\mu}^{\prime}+E_{\nu}^{\prime}\right)^{2}-c^{2}\left(\mathbf{p}_{\mu}^{\prime}+\mathbf{p}_{\nu}^{\prime}\right)^{2} \\
&=\left(\sqrt{c^{2} p_{\mu}^{\prime 2}+m_{\mu}^{2} c^{4}}+E_{\nu}^{\prime}\right)^{2} \\
&=2 c^{2} p_{\nu}^{\prime 2}+m_{\mu}^{2} c^{4}+2 c p_{\nu}^{\prime} \sqrt{c^{2} p_{\nu}^{\prime 2}+m_{\mu}^{2} c^{4}}
\end{aligned}
$$

When performing the above calculation, we used

$$
\mathbf{p}_{\mu}^{\prime}=-\mathbf{p}_{\nu}^{\prime}, \quad p_{\mu}^{\prime}=p_{\nu}^{\prime}, \quad E_{\nu}^{\prime}=c p_{\nu}^{\prime}
$$

From the above equation, we can solve for

$$
\begin{aligned}
p_{\nu}^{\prime} &= \frac{\left(m_{\pi}^{2}-m_{\mu}^{2}\right) c}{2 m_{\pi}} \\
E_{\nu}^{\prime} &= c p_{\nu}^{\prime} = \frac{\left(m_{\pi}^{2}-m_{\mu}^{2}\right) c^{2}}{2 m_{\pi}} = \frac{\left(m_{\pi} c^{2}\right)^{2}-\left(m_{\mu} c^{2}\right)^{2}}{2 m_{\pi} c^{2}} = \frac{(140)^{2}-(106)^{2}}{2 \times 140} = 29.9 \mathrm{MeV}
\end{aligned}
$$

方法一：在 \( S \) 系中历时 \( \Delta t \)，而在 \( S^{\prime} \) 系中的观察者看来，\( S \) 系的钟是动钟，由动钟变慢效应，应历时为 \( \Delta t^{\prime} \sqrt{1-\left(\frac{v}{c}\right)^{2}} \)。故在他看来，\( B \) 处的钟比 \( A \) 处的钟拨快的时间为

\[
\begin{aligned}
\delta & = \Delta t - \Delta t^{\prime} \sqrt{1-\left(\frac{v}{c}\right)^{2}} = \Delta t^{\prime}\left[\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-\left(\frac{v}{c}\right)^{2}}} - \sqrt{1-\left(\frac{v}{c}\right)^{2}}\right] \\
& = \frac{\Delta t^{\prime}\left(\frac{v}{c}\right)^{2}}{\sqrt{1-\left(\frac{v}{c}\right)^{2}}} = 18 \, \text{min}
\end{aligned}
\]

方法二：直接用拨快量公式

\[
\delta = \frac{v}{c^{2}} \Delta x = \frac{v}{c^{2}} \Delta L = \frac{0.6c}{c^{2}} \times 5.4 \times 10^{11} = 1.06 \times 10^{3} \, \text{s} = 18 \, \text{min}
\]

证明 12.2.1 题中将质点在 \(S^{\prime}\) 系中的速率 \(v^{\prime}\) 改为光速 \(c\), 即得要证明的第一个式子。这里为得出第二个式子。重新证明如下：

\[
\begin{gathered}
v_{x} = \frac{v_{x}^{\prime} + V}{1 + \frac{V}{c^{2}} v_{x}^{\prime}} = \frac{c \cos \theta^{\prime} + V}{1 + \frac{V}{c} \cos \theta^{\prime}} \\
v_{y} = \frac{v_{y}^{\prime} \sqrt{1-\left(\frac{V}{c}\right)^{2}}}{1+\frac{V}{c^{2}} v_{x}^{\prime}} = \frac{c \sin \theta^{\prime} \sqrt{1-\left(\frac{V}{c}\right)^{2}}}{1+\frac{V}{c} \cos \theta^{\prime}}
\end{gathered}
\]

